response.overview: April 25th, 2009 :: Partners and friends must fight in the Atomicos Increibles! The F.I.S.T. and Colony rivalry escalates to a fever pitch. Jimmy “Equinox” Olsen defends his Young Lions Cup against his fraternal twin brother Colin Delaney! Mike Quackenbush and Jigsaw receive their los Campeonatos de Parejas match in the main event, against The Osirian Portal! Matches featured:  1. 2.0 vs Incoherence  2. Nevaeh vs Shark Girl  3. Escorpion Egipcio vs Helios  4. Player Uno, Hydra, Vin Gerard & Buck Hawke vs Player Dos, Brodie Lee, Tim Donst & STIGMA  5. Shadow Phoenix vs Gran Akuma  6. F.I.S.T. vs The Colony  7. Young Lions Cup Match Colin Delaney vs Equinox  8. Campeonatos de Parejas Match The Osirian Portal vs Jigsaw & Mike Quackenbush
response.title: Chikara Behind The 8-Ball
